Description: AI Shell standalone binaries and sandbox service
 AI Shell is an interactive shell with built-in LLM capabilities.
 This package ships prebuilt PyInstaller binaries for the main CLI and the
 privileged sandbox daemon, along with the default security policy, bundled
 skills, and systemd unit files.
